-8b04-4ef3f795f24d.png)\r\n\r\nthe server log says this:\r\n\r\n{\"app\":\"php\",\"message\":\"copy(\\/var\\/www\\/html\\/owncloud\\/data\\/admin\\/documents\\/519c065921b8f7d12066c7d1817703f3e728ab51.odt): failed to open stream: no such file or directory at \\/var\\/www\\/html\\/owncloud\\/lib\\/private\\/files\\/storage\\/local.php#184\",\"level\":2,\"time\":\"2013-11-08t11:07:30+00:00\"}\r\n{\"app\":\"documents\",\"message\":\"starting a session failed. reason: failed to copy genesis\",\"level\":2,\"time\":\"2013-11-08t11:07:30+00:00\"}\r\n\r\nso i manually created the documents directory on the user's account (\"admin\"):\r\n\r\nmkdir /var/www/html/owncloud/data/admin/documents\r\nchown apache:apache /var/www/html/owncloud/data/admin/documents\r\n\r\n and bingo - it works.\r\n","closed_by":{"login":"vicdeo","id":991300,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/57b8c1e26d502d5414e4b2fb875d2994?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2fe8357fefe8bad5436de368fa5a419461.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"57b8c1e26d502d5414e4b2fb875d2994","url":"https://api.github.com/users/vicdeo","html_url":"https://github.com/vicdeo","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/vicdeo/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/vicdeo/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/vicdeo/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/vicdeo/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/vicdeo/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/vicdeo/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/vicdeo/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/vicdeo/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/vicdeo/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false}}